<p>Suppose at a university someone wants to replicate a study, but with greater power. Which of the following statements about this is correct, assuming other circumstances remain the same?</p>
<p>I. The power of a test increases as the sample size increases. II. The power of a test increases if the probability of an error of the first kind is is reduced.</p>
</p>]]></text>
