<text><![CDATA[<p>
Neither proposition is correct.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="100" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Only statement I is correct.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
